headline: Trump limits Kellogg's role to Ukraine envoy after Russian complaints
summary: President Donald Trumpsaid on Saturday that General Keith Kellogg's role has beennarrowed from special envoy for Ukraine and Russia to onlyUkraine, after Russian officials had sought to exclude him...
